1. DEFINITIONS, PURPOSE & VISION
"The Software" refers to the qgate source code, documentation, simulation data, examples, and all associated files distributed in this repository.
The Software is released under this Source Available License to foster academic reproducibility, peer review, and transparent benchmarking of time-symmetric trajectory filtering on Noisy Intermediate-Scale Quantum (NISQ) hardware.

